BFN 

<F P=106> ["IPSOS/LE POINT" opinion poll on European elections] </F>
  [Text] A poll conducted 7-11 May of a national sample of 
1,000 persons representative of the French population aged 18 
and over, using face-to-face interviews, and based on the quota 
method, yielded the following answers on the upcoming European 
elections. 


